data.description: Charming end unit townhome in Morrow! This quaint residence features a cozy atmosphere with five rooms, including two bedrooms and two full baths. Enjoy the convenience of an end unit, offering extra privacy with a fenced in yard and natural light. The home boast a warm and inviting ambiance perfect for comfortable living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming townhome yours!
